  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Speed Sweeper </h2>A competitive minesweeper speed-runner!<br>With multiple game modes, daily challenges, and online leader boards.<br>Focused on enabling speed running, the game is tailored towards players of all skill sets.<br>Take full control over the size of the game board, and amount of bombs.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/224ca33df45111267817b5a1b5ad80d1.poster.avif?t=1583505941\" width=446 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/224ca33df45111267817b5a1b5ad80d1.webm?t=1583505941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/224ca33df45111267817b5a1b5ad80d1.mp4?t=1583505941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize the board</strong></h2>Set custom board sizes, bomb amount, themes and backgrounds.<br><br><strong>Game modes include:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic - Clear the board as fast as you can<br></li><li>Speed - Make each move before the timer runs out <br></li><li>Daily Challenge - Compete on the same board as everyone else<br></li><li>3 Lives - Mines don't instantly end the game.<br></li><li>Tower - Complete 5 levels in a row</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/3b3442a9a1798c5cf779fb4fb4c67e72.poster.avif?t=1583505941\" width=188 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/3b3442a9a1798c5cf779fb4fb4c67e72.webm?t=1583505941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/3b3442a9a1798c5cf779fb4fb4c67e72.mp4?t=1583505941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Speed Sweeper </h2>A competitive minesweeper speed-runner!<br>With multiple game modes, daily challenges, and online leader boards.<br>Focused on enabling speed running, the game is tailored towards players of all skill sets.<br>Take full control over the size of the game board, and amount of bombs.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/224ca33df45111267817b5a1b5ad80d1.poster.avif?t=1583505941\" width=446 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/224ca33df45111267817b5a1b5ad80d1.webm?t=1583505941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/224ca33df45111267817b5a1b5ad80d1.mp4?t=1583505941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize the board</strong></h2>Set custom board sizes, bomb amount, themes and backgrounds.<br><br><strong>Game modes include:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic - Clear the board as fast as you can<br></li><li>Speed - Make each move before the timer runs out <br></li><li>Daily Challenge - Compete on the same board as everyone else<br></li><li>3 Lives - Mines don't instantly end the game.<br></li><li>Tower - Complete 5 levels in a row</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/3b3442a9a1798c5cf779fb4fb4c67e72.poster.avif?t=1583505941\" width=188 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/3b3442a9a1798c5cf779fb4fb4c67e72.webm?t=1583505941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248680/extras/